# Cordova plugins for Capacitor
capacitor-cordova-ios-plugins

# NOTE: `App/App/public`, `App/App/capacitor.config.json`, and `App/App/config.xml` are
# intentionally NOT ignored so they can be committed. That lets Xcode builds work on
# machines that never run `npx cap copy ios` (e.g. rented VMs without npm). Refresh
# them locally with: `npm run ios:assets` from the repo root, then commit.
